## PolyAsyncIterable.concat() method

Return a new iteration that will iterate over `this`<!-- -->, then over `other`<!-- -->.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
concat<U>(other: Iterable<U> | AsyncIterable<U>): PolyAsyncIterable<T | U>;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  other | Iterable&lt;U&gt; \| AsyncIterable&lt;U&gt; | Iterable to be appended |

<b>Returns:</b>

PolyAsyncIterable&lt;T \| U&gt;

a new [PolySyncIterable](./polyethylene.polysynciterable.md) that yields the elements of `this` and then the elements of `other`
